          </h2>
          <div class="relative">
            <!-- Timeline line -->
            <div class="absolute left-4 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-neon-lime/20"></div>
            
            <!-- Timeline items -->
            <div class="space-y-10">
              <div class="relative flex items-start">
                <div class="absolute left-2 top-2 w-4 h-4 bg-neon-lime rounded-full border-2 border-matrix-black shadow-neon"></div>
                <div class="ml-12">
                  <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-3">
                    <span class="text-sm text-matrix-white/60">2024 - Present</span>
                    <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-neon-lime/10 text-neon-lime text-xs rounded">Current</span>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="font-orbitron font-bold text-neon-lime mb-2 text-shadow-neon text-lg">Senior QA Automation Specialist</h3>
