                  </div>
                  <h3 class="font-orbitron font-bold text-digital-emerald mb-2 text-shadow-emerald text-lg">Full-Stack Developer & Project Lead</h3>
                  <p class="text-neon-lime text-base mb-3">Casa Capoeira - Modern CMS Platform</p>
                  <p class="text-matrix-white/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
